snippet.title: FREEDOM CONVOY 2022 | Truckers To The Rescue! | "A Small Fringe Minority with UNNACCEPTABLE VIEWS!?"
snippet.description:
The truckers have now arrived in the capital at Parliament Hill, Ottawa. I share my thoughts of what has so far transpired in regards to the 2022 Truckers Freedom Convoy.

♪MY ORIGINAL SONG "CRAZY" ABOUT COVID, MENTAL HEALTH AND FREEDOM♪👇https://youtu.be/BYDTsTAOEL8
